Description: Replace system gzip with gzippy (fast parallel gzip)
 This package replaces the system gzip, gunzip, gzcat, and zcat commands
 with gzippy, providing significantly faster compression and decompression.
 .
 When installed, all system gzip operations will use gzippy transparently.
 This is fully compatible with standard gzip - files compressed with gzippy
 can be decompressed by any standard gzip implementation.
 .
 WARNING: This package conflicts with and replaces the gzip package.
 Install only if you want gzippy to handle all gzip operations system-wide.

